title: Samsung Dishwasher Affresh Cleaner
description: Samsung Dishwasher Affresh Cleaner PartSelect Number PS2367638 Manufacturer Part Number W10282479 There are 6 tablets in each package and it is suggested to use every month. These keep the dishwasher fresh by dissolving and removing odor.

installationInstructions.author: Carmen from Milton, DE
installationInstructions.title: Replace lower dishwasher rack……. Plastic rusting
installationInstructions.content: Open box ….. pull out new rack ….. roll out old rack  - roll in new rack
